column5: but I saw an article in today's Toronto Sun about this new C&R record from the St. Larry back in November?  http://www.torontosun.com/news/canada/2009...789376-sun.html

Yeah, it was posted and Dale MacNair has replied to most posts about it.  Hey, don't get me wrong it's a GREAT FISH so I'm not hear to rain on your post of a new finding.  After all, I think you can see Dale MacNair and the mount of the fish this Sat. at the show in TO!
